<br>
I've had a bard slower and tank quite a few times in HoH. Usually that was with a druid healer too.<br>
<br>
You talk about singing posthaste and Rizlona... Rizlona IS posthaste.<br>
<br>
You talk about 21 hp regen, that's the mana regen. Hp regen uses the singing mods from equipment, AA and buffs. So an epic bard with Voice of the serpent and a few AAs gets that regen to somewhere around 80 hp/tick.<br>
<br>
Concerning damage making, bards usually support damage from the others rather than making their own, but if required they can do decent damage. Ok they won't outdamage a wizard, but if at least 2 are in a group, they can use many songs together, and therefore use the more damage oriented songs. Even one bard gets me over 100 DS when I go help friends through the Exe trial, so we don't slow waves to increase our chances. And if you think PoP charmed mobs don't make damage... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=throes>Throes</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.harmonium.net/filespace/throes/FIRE.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Flintnilf the Wise</font></td></tr></table></span><br>  Posts: 121<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/28/03 8:10:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25537.topic&index=18>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.harmonium.net/ports/sm-flintnilf.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re:</span><hr size=1> I would kill for about 5 more bards in my guild. Can't tell you why on raids, but if you don't know, I won't tell you. Groups? Bard in the group means Rizlona's, manasong, CC, non stop casting and huge crits. <br>
